data.description: Exquisitely Updated Residence in Prestigious Tallyns Reach on a Very Private Cul-De-Sac! This home has been completely transformed top to bottom into a masterpiece with mature landscaping and a wrap around front porch. Inside you are greeted by a stunning vaulted foyer, white-oak style hickory flooring, and sweeping wrought iron staircase. Large picture windows with plantation shutters stream in natural light, and built-in surround sound is featured in many rooms. The formal entertaining room welcomes you with custom wainscoting and crown molding, and the formal dining room with butler's pantry can host special events for years to come. The gourmet chef's kitchen has been highly upgraded with a large center island with prep sink, quartz counters, soft close cabinetry with under cabinet lighting, GE Monogram appliance suite with French door fridge, range hood, double ovens/Advantium convection oven, walk-in pantry, and an abundance of counter and cabinet space for prep and storage. A main floor office with French doors and feature wall makes a perfect, private retreat. The vaulted 2-story family room with 3-sided stone fireplace, shiplap nook, and built-in details wows. The sumptuous primary suite has a custom wainscoting detail at the headboard, striking chandelier, and French doors that lead to a private deck. Unwind in the spa-like bathroom with jetted tub, dual vanities, oversized shower with decorative tile, and massive walk-in closet. The loft provides a functional homework/home office space. 3 very spacious secondary bedrooms have either private en-suite or Jack-and-Jill bath access. The outdoor living space is a private and tranquil entertainer's delight with an expansive stamped concrete patio with surround sound. Located in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods, this home offers close proximity to the finest amenities the Denver Metro area has to offer, walking distance to schools. This extraordinary home sets a new standard for luxury living!
